        <p>Student-provided answers to homework set #1, due date unspecified (not to be handed in and thus not marked). The content on this page is solely intended to function as a study aid for students and should constitute fair dealing under Canadian copyright law.</p>
<p>Problems to complete: (2.1) #1-12, (2.2) #1-13,16,17, (2.3) #1-14, (2.4) #1-8, #13-19, (2.5) #1-13, (3.1) #1-18, (3.2) #1-23, (3.3) #1-12, (3.4) #1-16 (omit limsup and liminf), (3.5) #1-11 (omit contractive sequences), (3.6) #1-10. </p>
